logic.misc

Class ConfigLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.misc.ConfigLoader

  • public class ConfigLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    ConfigLoader is used to load the config.file into the system. The config.file also contains the names of the tables and columns of the database, if a specific implementation of the server requires a similar database, however with other table and column names

        private static final ConfigLoader SINGLETON
        Not more than one ConfigLoader can be instantiated, why it is a SINGLETON. The ConfigLoader HAS to be instantiated, before the static variables can be called.
